The image_editing skill provides the `convert` command from ImageMagick. I can use this to convert images to grayscale. Let me convert the keyframes to grayscale.

```json
{
  "analysis": "The image_editing skill provides the `convert` command from ImageMagick. I can use this to convert images to grayscale. I'll convert each keyframe to grayscale in-place.",
  "plan": "Use the `convert` command to convert each keyframe to grayscale. The command should be: `convert keyframes_*.png -colorspace gray keyframes_*.png`. This will convert all keyframes to grayscale in-place.",
  "commands": [
    {
      "keystrokes": "convert /root/keyframes_*.png -colorspace gray /root/keyframes_*.png\n",
      "duration": 1.0
    }
  ]
}
```
